{
  "texts": [
    "Nonetheless, having abundant training data to unlock its immense potential is crucial.",
    "Unfortunately, there is currently a scarcity of publicly available datasets that are sufficiently large for time series forecasting.",
    "Most existing pre-trained time-series models use public datasets like Traffic and Electricity.",
    "Despite these benchmark datasets serving as the foundation for developing time series forecasting, their limited size and lack of generalizability pose significant challenges for large-scale pre-training.",
    "Thus, in the context of time-series prediction, the most pressing matter is the development of expansive and highly generalized datasets (similar to ImageNet in computer vision)."
  ]
}